snippet.title: Project Paradise 2 - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Project Paradise 2 is an online mod for Test Drive Unlimited 2, which brings back many multiplayer features that we've been missing in the last couple years. 
Website: https://www.project-paradise2.de/
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/PTVmbq8mpC

My inspiration for this trailer came from The Grand Tour opening.
Almost all clips you see are recorded by myself, except the ones of the Casino - these are from the original Casino trailer.

If you want to use my footage for your own video, feel free to do so however please mention my channel.
